text.autoconfig.onebar.option.goodThings:
Shows an indicator when you have invisibility effect;
crosses it out when wearing armor/offhand item,
have glowing effect or arrow(s) stuck in you.

text.autoconfig.onebar.option.armor.show:
Shows an indicator when wearing a skeleton, creeper or
zombie mob head; carved pumpkin; any golden armor item.
Worn mob heads reduce respective mob detection range by 50%;
carved pumpkin will prevent aggrevating endermen by looking;
any golden armor item will prevent piglin aggrevation.
